OL,3,CKate Garraway says it was 'honour and
OL,4,Cprivilege' to care for late husband
OL,6,FThe presenter made an appearance on
OL,7,FITV's Good Morning Britain, just three
OL,8,Fdays after laying her husband to rest
OL,10,Fdescribed it as an "honour and
OL,11,Fprivilege" to care for her late
OL,12,Fhusband Derek Draper following his
OL,13,Ffuneral.
OL,15,FThe presenter made an appearance on
OL,16,FITV's Good Morning Britain on Monday
OL,17,Fmorning, just three days after laying
OL,18,Fher husband to rest in London.
