OL,3,CKate Garraway says it was 'honour and
OL,4,Cprivilege' to care for late husband
OL,6,FIn the interview, she spoke of her
OL,7,F"outpouring of love for everyone that
OL,8,Fhas supported me" and spoke of
OL,9,Fsplitting her time between being a
OL,10,Fmother to her children as well as
OL,11,Fbeing a wife and carer for Draper.
OL,13,F"I think for people watching that are
OL,14,Fcarers, they will know two things: how
OL,15,Funbelievably hard it is but what an
OL,16,Fhonour it is too."
OL,18,FThrough tears, she added: "You know, I
OL,19,Fwish I was caring today."
