OL,3,CKate Garraway says it was 'honour and
OL,4,Cprivilege' to care for late husband
OL,6,FDraper fell seriously ill with Covid-
OL,7,F19 during the early part of the
OL,8,Fpandemic in March 2020 and spent 13
OL,9,Fmonths in hospital before he was
OL,10,Fdischarged.
OL,12,FHe died on January 3, aged 56, after
OL,13,Fsuffering long-lasting symptoms from
OL,14,Fcoronavirus.
OL,16,FGarraway also shared that she was told
OL,17,FDraper had 24 hours to live a month
OL,18,Fbefore he eventually died.
