OL,3,CKate Garraway says it was 'honour and
OL,4,Cprivilege' to care for late husband
OL,6,FShe also discussed her 17-year-old
OL,7,Fdaughter Darcey's role as a pallbearer
OL,8,Fat the service, saying: "She insisted
OL,9,Fon doing it and I thought it was a
OL,10,Fbeautiful thing."
OL,12,FOf Darcey and son Billy, 12, she
OL,13,Fadded: "For their grieving, we are in
OL,14,Fthe foothills, we know there is a long
OL,15,Fway to go."
OL,17,FShe continued: "They didn't want to
OL,18,Fpressure him to keep going. I don't
OL,19,Fthink he did feel that, I think he
OL,20,Fkept going because he wanted to be
OL,21,Fhere."
