OL,6,FGarraway confirmed she will return to
OL,7,Fthe desk on GMB on Thursday and joked:
OL,8,F"I'm going to be looking forward to a
OL,9,Fblow dry."
OL,11,FShe said she will also be cracking out
OL,12,Fthe fake eyelashes and fake tan,
OL,13,Fadding: "Don't worry ` I am going to
OL,14,Fbe looking a lot more respectable."
OL,16,FShe went on: "I am looking forward to
OL,17,Fcoming into the world and connecting
OL,18,Fwith everyone again.
